  "title": "The Ring and Lilo & Stitch actress Daveigh Chase dies aged 35",
  "description": "Chase died from sepsis following a bout with meningitis in a Los Angeles hospital, her longtime manager told the BBC.",
  "text": "Daveigh Chase, the horror actress. crawled out of a telly in The. Ring and. voiced Lilo in Disney's animated Lilo & Stitch, has died aged 35. Chase. also starred in the cable drama Big Love, died from sepsis. Following a bout with meningitis in a Los Angeles hospital, her longtime. Manager John Ryan Jr confirmed to BBC News on Wednesday. Ryan said that Chase had been admitted to hospital for malnourishment before her death. The former child star began acting at 4 years old, booking her. First Hollywood job when she was 7, but. She retired from acting full time in 2015, he said.",
